<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.11">
<l>kēṭil viḻuppukaḻk kēcava ṉaikkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉcoṉṉa</l>
<l>pāṭalō rāyirat tuḷivai pattum payiṟṟaval lārkkava</l>
<l>ṉāṭu nakaramu naṉkuṭaṉ kāṇa nalaṉiṭai yūrtipaṇṇi</l>
<l>vīṭum peṟuttitaṉ mūvula kukkun tarumoru nāyakamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To those able to repeat these ten among the one thousand songs</l>
<l>composed by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr on Keśava of lossless excellent fame</l>
<l>he will give sole leadership of his three worlds, making [them] obtain liberation,</l>
<l>making a vehicle inside goodness so that they well see both his land and hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
